Old Dominion Capital Management, Inc. is a registered investment advisory firm with offices in Charlottesville and Alexandria, Virginia. We offer integrated investment management and financial planning services primarily to families and individuals. As your financial partner, our job is to provide individualized, customized strategies to help you achieve financial independence, security, and freedom. 
Our clients include professionals, business executives, entrepreneurs, retirees, trusts, surviving spouses, and spouses in transition from divorce, as well as families, endowments, and foundations committed to achieving their financial goals. 
As a fee-only investment advisory firm, Old Dominion Capital Management, Inc. does not receive commissions on any securities or products. We focus on selecting investments and appropriate strategies to uniquely serve each client. We also work with complementary financial professionals, including CPAs and estate planning attorneys, to provide customized solutions for our clients. 
Contact us today at 434-977-1550 to learn more about how our firm and services can help you reach your financial goals, simplify the often-confusing investment process, and provide thoughtful financial guidance.
             
 
                                                             










 













